# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ATLAS Corporation — security-first .gitignore (commit #1)
# The fund-moving surface is the attack surface. Nothing secret enters git.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Secrets, keys, wallets — NEVER commit
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.key
*.pem
*.p12
*.pfx
*.keystore
*.mnemonic
*.seed
secrets/
wallets/
keystore/
keys/
**/okx_sa*.json
**/*passphrase*
**/*secret*
policy/owner-config.local.json
policy/*.secret.json

# OKX / Virtuals / signer material
OKX_API_KEY*
OKX_SECRET*
OKX_PASSPHRASE*
*.signer.json
privy_*.json

# External repos cloned only to STUDY — never vendor into this repo
**/_clones/
research/_clones/
acp_tracer/research/_clones/

# Node / build
node_modules/
dist/
build/
.next/
out/
coverage/
.turbo/
*.tsbuildinfo

# Python (if an engine uses it)
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
venv/

# Runtime state — agent memory / ledger / logs (never in git)
*.log
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.db
runtime/state/
update.local.md

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp

# OnchainOS / OKX skill (project-scoped) — never commit skills, fetched binaries, or wallet/session state
.agents/
skills-lock.json
.claude/skills/
.onchainos/
onchainos-*
okx-pilot*
*.session

# ATLAS soul upload — never commit the wallet key or per-session env
soul/*.key
